', 'What is this life but a series of obstacles? The good news is nothing happens without the Almightyâ€™s Will. If anything unpleasant comes into your life, it had to get approval from Him. He knows the kind of test you need. Heâ€™s placed a blessing inside of it. Itâ€™s for your good!

', 'Anger is a choice. We can choose to retreat into our own minds and calm down or we can explode. Anger takes a lot of energy. Fighting, using derogatory words and showing acts of violence donâ€™t solve any problem. Instead, take a step back, rationalise and seek the Almightyâ€™s help!
